citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:00pm on 08-
February-2023.
The inspector arrived at the facility at 2:00 pm and knocked on the door to the house, called and left a message, honked
the horn of the vehicle, waited 30 minutes and then left the facility.
